Package view

Interface FeatureReceiver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Language, StaticView
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    View
    public interface FeatureReceiver
extends StaticView, Language
    This interface follows the observer design pattern. This is given to classes which implement the Feature interface so that there can be two way communication between the View and the features
    Author:
    Ben Lawrence, Khian Wei Goh
